create_account_and_enjoy: Create an account to enjoy our services!
description_1:
This is a open source project to help musicians to make songs, programmers to get
					inspired, thinkers to start writing posts, designers to make web-sites, and read posts all
					in one application. You can always join our project and help create mixes, new web
					features and implement bug fixes and much more!
open_source_desc: Open source platform, made from open source tech.
everything_in_one_place: Everything you need all in one place
find_people:
Find people, knowledge base and inspiration to create what you want. Make decisions based on
				what YOU need and find what's best for you.
weite_tech_posts:
Write technical posts and knowledge for everyone to see. We provide a simple to use
							and beautiful text editor to share what you know.
become_a_studio_description:
Become a mixing studio and create services for users. Currently we are looking for all
							types of engineers. You can apply for admin in your profile page.
open_source_desc_2:
We use open source to innovate our services. Never get locked in or discontinued
							again! You can always join our community and start submitting features your self.
contact_us_desc:
If you have any issues with your current work that you think we can help you with, make
						sure to contact us.
record_audio_desc: Contact our audio engineering team to book a recording session.
mix_audio_desc: Pick and choose an audio engineer to mix and master your song professionally.
producing_desc: A list full of beat makers that are willing to create with you.
become_mixing_engineer_desc:
If you are interested in helping others with their songs, make sure to contact us as we
						do look out for our own.
join_comm_desc: If you are just passing by, make sure to leave a funny comment or post.
beginner_desc:
We provide many tutorials and resources to get started in music production, programming,
					philosophy, advertising and more! Join our community to create posts and tutorials for
					beginners.
thoughtfully_designed_for: Thoughtfully designed for the musicians, business, and artists.
create_account_and_start:
Create an account and start reading, liking, commenting. You can also apply for our admin to
				create services.
we_record_and_track: We record and track the progress that we make everyday.
the_latest_news: The latest news, articles, and resources, sent to your inbox weekly.
user_profile_description: Your profile will be visible to the studios, put some data in there ❤️
user_posts_description: Your posts will be visible to everyone. Share your thoughts and get feedback
no_reports_description: Get started by using our service!
